### 5. Listening on all interfaces with hardcoded port, no TLS (A02, A05)
`app.listen(3000)` binds `0.0.0.0` and serves cleartext HTTP. For anything beyond localhost, terminate TLS at a reverse proxy (nginx, ALB) and:
```js
